    "text": "Addressing Social Isolation and Loneliness in Older Adults Act of 2021 or the Addressing SILO Act of 2021\n\nThis bill provides funding through FY2025 for grants to prevent and address social isolation or loneliness among older adults and individuals with disabilities through education, outreach, and interventions. The Department of Health and Human Services must award these grants to area agencies on aging and community-based organizations."
